quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  17,85,"Uye vanokubvunza (Muhammad (SAW)) maereano neRooh (Mweya). Iti: “Rooh (Mweya) chimwe chezvinhu, ruzivo rwayo rwuna Tenzi vangu. Uye hamuna kupihwa ruzivo kusara kwerwushoma.”"
  17,86,"Uye dai takada, zvirokwazvo, dai takatora izvo zvatakadzikisa kwauri (Qur’aan). Naizvozvo waishaiwa muchengeti nazvo kubva kwatiri"
  17,87,"Kunze kwetsitsi kubva kuna Tenzi vako. Zvirokwazvo, nyasha dzavo kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) izhinji"
  17,88,"Iti: “Kunyangwe vanhu nemaJinn vakaungana kugadzira zvakafanana neQur’aan iri, havagadziri zvakafanana naro, kunyangwe vamwe vavo vakabetsera vamwe.”"
  17,89,"Uye zvirokwazvo, takatsanangurira vanhu muQur’aan iri mienzaniso yese, asi vanhu vazhinji vanoramba (Chokwadi) kusara kwekusatenda"
  17,90,"Uye vanoti: “Hatitendi mauri (Muhammad (SAW)) kusvika watiburitsira chitubu panyika.”"
  17,91,"“Kana kuti une bindu remadheti nemagirepu, uye unoita nzizi dziyerere pakati paro.”"
  17,92,"“Kana kudonhedza denga muzvidimbu sekutiudza (sekunyengedza) kwawakatiita, kana kuunza Allah nengirozi kwatiri.”"
  17,93,"“Kana kuti ova neimba yeZukhruf (Sirivha negoridhe), kana kuti okwira kudenga, uye hatimbotendi mukukwira kwako kusvika wadzikisa kwatiri gwaro kuti tiverenge.” Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Kurumbidzwa ngakuve kuna Tenzi vangu! Ndingave chimwe chinhu here asi munhu akatumirwa semutumwa?”"